The '''Ancient vestment set''' is a [[members]] [[item set]] of [[Armour/Prayer armour|Prayer armour]] aligned with [[Zaros]]. The pieces are only obtainable by completing [[Clue scroll (easy)|easy]] and [[Clue scroll (medium)|medium]] [[Treasure Trail]]s.

==Requirements==
Equipping the whole set requires 60 [[Prayer]] and 40 [[Magic]], however, each piece has its own requirements:
